    "Prognostic models using DL can be used to predict the remaining useful life of medical devices.",
    "These models can help healthcare providers plan for the maintenance and replacement of medical devices before they fail.",
    "Predictive maintenance scheduling using DL can help healthcare providers optimize maintenance schedules based on the predicted failure rates of medical devices.",
    "This can help reduce downtime and improve the reliability of medical devices.",
    "Fault diagnosis using DL can help healthcare providers quickly identify and diagnose issues with medical devices."
